=== Transitive verb ===
'''to open''' ([[opens]], [[opened]], [[opening]])
# the action of making something accessible or removing an obstacle to something being accessible (e.g. opening a door to access the room behind it).
# to bring up (a topic). (''I don't want to open that subject.'')
# to prepare (an establishment) to conduct business.  (''I will open the shop an hour early tomorrow.'')
# To start (a campaign)

